        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Political Pay Raises During Shutdowns Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Vice President and certain senior political appointees at federal agencies from receiving a pay increase during any lapse in appropriations beginning on or after December 22, 2018. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
